====================================================================
MAP INFO
====================================================================

Map                   : gg_cubes
Game                  : Counter-Strike: Source
Game type             : Gun Game
Recommended Players  : 10-20
Description           : An outdoor map set on floating cube-like 
                            structures.  Various levels and catwalks.  To access the  
                             top orange catwalk, you must travel to the bottom where 
                            a semi-tall multi-colored cube is and jump on top of it.   
                            This will teleport you to the top.

====================================================================
INSTALLATION
====================================================================

Place gg_cubes in your Steam\SteamApps\youremailaddress\
counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.

====================================================================
CONTACT
